# Generated voice + raw screencast binaries live in public/ for Remotion's
# staticFile() to resolve. They're large and reproducible, so we don't
# track them — regenerate voice via `npm run voice`, drop screencasts in
# from Screen Studio. Music (brand-track + logo-sting) is user-supplied
# from a royalty-free source — see public/audio/music/README.md.
public/audio/**/*.wav
public/audio/**/*.mp3
public/audio/**/*.m4a
public/audio/audition/
public/screencasts/

